dct_title_s: Burritt's sectional and township map of Minnesota
dct_description_sm: Shows U.S. land offices and boundaries of land districts.Relief shown by hachures.Hand colored.Includes "Table of distances by railroad and steamboat lines in Minnesota" and 2 vignettes. Dimensions: 88 x 80 centimeters
